reviews.author: Laura Pfister
reviews.text: Unforgettable experience!! It was one of the craziest but best things I‘ve done in my life - would 100% recommend it!! My instructor was Rhys, he was very friendly and funny which made the moments before the jump a little less scary - thanks again! Would 100% do it again!

reviews.author: Rosie North
reviews.text: Had the best experience doing my skydive this morning. I was paired with Shaun and he couldn’t have been more amazing. I was very nervous and he reassured me. Had the best time would recommend 100%

reviews.author: Xinyong Chen
reviews.text: A nearly perfect skydiving experience, they provided on-time airport pick-up and drop-off service, the instructor was very responsible and provided clear teaching. After take-off, you can see the magnificent island scenery and enjoy the soaring experience like a bird.

reviews.author: Customer
reviews.text: I was my first skydiving and it was amazing ! I jumped with Zac and he was amazing ! I felt really safe and in good hands and he took really nice pictures and videos. It’s my best memory in my life ! I want to do it again !!! See you soon !

reviews.author: Mark Campbell
reviews.text: Staffs here were very nice! I am really bad at English and ignored one of them's encouragement, I just smiled. Also,I did not distinguish left from right, which seemed to cause some trouble to the staff. I am very sorry. Hope they can see, I loved skydiving and will definitely do it again, all thanks to the wonderful staff here

reviews.author: Isabelle Jones
reviews.text: Such a phenomenal experience! We had our jump at 7am and it was the BEST start to any day. Reece was the best guide ever, I felt so safe and still had so much fun - would recommend to anyone!

reviews.author: Dona Mallik
reviews.text: Once in a lifetime enriched by the confidence and prowess of tandem masters, and all others who received us, instructed us, geared us up, flew us up to 15 K feet, and shuttled us back from the landing area. The pics would speak for themselves - the thrill, the views, the safety measures!

reviews.author: Abigail Jones
reviews.text: Amazing experience! Check in was made quick and easy. Instructors were all lovely, relaxed and made us feel at ease. Aiden my instructor was brilliant, talking me through the dive and made the experience a lot less scary!Thank you

reviews.author: Alicia Boyle
reviews.text: Wow - this was my second skydive and it was incredible. Airlie Beach is definitely up there with one of the best views in the world! Thank you instructor Jamie - I had the best time :) I will be back!!

reviews.author: Maya Chan
reviews.text: I really enjoyed my experience with skydive airlie beach. With this being my first skydive, my instructor Mo was very friendly, informative and made me feel at ease during my dive. The whole team and experience is a genuine 5 stars and would recommend to anyone looking to book!

reviews.author: Leire Etxebarria
reviews.text: I had the best time!! I jumped with Zac, and he was absolutely amazing. Jamie also jumped with us and made me feel so safe and comfortable. They both were so fun and made the whole experience unforgettable! 100% recommend doing it!!
